Options -Indexes

# cPanel Node.js deployment:
# 1. Build frontend:  cd hcc && npm run build
# 2. Copy build:      cp -r hcc/dist/* hccbackend/public/
# 3. Setup Node.js App: startup file = app.js, root = hccbackend folder
# 4. Set .env: NODE_ENV=production, RUN_SCHEMA_INIT=false, cPanel MySQL credentials
# 5. Run npm install in hccbackend, then Restart app
